21:15.470 --> 21:17.358
Holmes gave us.
Abigail was being tailed

21:17.410 --> 21:19.366
by a private investigator
out of Trenton.

21:19.410 --> 21:20.707
We just talked to the guy.

21:20.740 --> 21:22.628
Turns out he was hired
by none other

21:22.680 --> 21:24.898
