22:02.120 --> 22:04.338
at the Bedford house
with the boys the other night,

22:04.390 --> 22:05.789
but once we spoke to them
on their own,

22:05.820 --> 22:07.515
they said they were
watching TV in their rooms.

22:07.560 --> 22:09.482
It wouldn't have been hard
for her to sneak out,

22:09.520 --> 22:11.488
poison Titus, and make it back
before anyone noticed.

22:11.530 --> 22:14.021
So it looks like
Sherlock was right;

22:14.060 --> 22:16.824
Abigail was being framed.

22:16.860 --> 22:19.567
My client is ready
to make a statement.

22:21.570 --> 22:24.664
The night Titus died,
I met Dr. Phillip Malone

22:24.710 --> 22:27.634
at the Campbell Bar
in Mount Kisco as 7:00 pm.

22:27.680 --> 22:28.806
